    "body": "Thanks for raising this issue @segersb . We're aware of it and have a proposed fix awaiting review. \r\nA temporary workaround is to explicitly define `global` in the REPL: \r\n```\r\nglobal = this \r\n```\r\nNote: `globalThis` is not available in node 10",
